<p><span id="more-115232"></span></p>
<p>Released on Quest in October, <em>Dungeons of Eternity </em>includes both co-op and solo gameplay, pitting you against ever-changing dungeons with up to three other players.</p>
<p>The game&#8217;s randomly-generated dungeons also include multiple game modes and realms, featuring stuff like combat arenas, puzzles, trap rooms, secret chambers, and more—basically everything you&#8217;d expect from a DnD-style VR game.</p>
<p>At any rate, that&#8217;s what the game launched with a little over a month ago, but now <a href="https://twitter.com/DungeonsVR/status/1727011401489961322" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the studio says</a> it has a bunch of new content on the horizon, as the studio released a roadmap projecting clear out to the end of next year. Check it out below:</p>
<figure id="attachment_115236" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-115236" src="https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024.jpg 1200w, https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024-125x70.jpg 125w, https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024-320x180.jpg 320w, https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024-768x432.jpg 768w, https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024-640x360.jpg 640w, https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024-747x420.jpg 747w, https://roadtovrlive-5ea0.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dungeons-eternity-map-2024-681x383.jpg 681w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Image courtesy Othergate</figcaption></figure>
<p>Studio co-founder Ryan Rutherford also says in a recent <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/DungeonsOfEternityVR/comments/181jio2/dungeons_of_eternity_ama_with_the_dev_team/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reddit AMA</a> that the team has a &#8220;precise vision of creating a long-lasting VR experience you can enjoy with your friends or by yourself,&#8221; noting that the studio is entertaining a host of other improvements beyond those mentioned above.</p>

<p>You can find it on the <a href="https://www.meta.com/en-gb/experiences/6341779295861881/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Meta Store for Quest</a>, priced at $30. At the time of this writing, <em>Dungeons of Eternity</em> is sporting a [4.65/5] user rating.</p>
